Package to.us.resume_builder.business.export_LaTeX

Interface ILaTeXConvertable

All Known Implementing Classes:
Bullet, BulletCategory, Category, Experience, ExperienceCategory, HeaderCategory, TextCategory
public interface ILaTeXConvertable
Implementing this interface indicates that the class is LaTeX-serializable through the use of a ResumeTemplate.
Author:
Matthew McCaskill
